data.message: You ain't a winna You a basic beginner niggas like you get eatin like steak in dinner . That's two chains but I'm wearing 3 of em game on lock like my Rolex watch time does talk and so does money texas my name man it feels lovely . I can hold jelwery of shine like Bonnie and Clyde but I don't roll like that cause it's my time to shine . I'm from Texas foo respect that with first verse that hurts that could leave you in that e-r for fucking with that boy e-l-m straight to that e-r. Not vicious like mike but I ain't scared to fight. type like that just seem to bite quit taking my shine and hop of my grind . Cause in block we don't play ,fuck around and introduce you to that snap back with yo hallow chain jacked .im reckless like 3 DUIs with Chinese eyes spiced of 2d guide but this nigga out of his mind  .mama told me once if you gonna die don't die a coward die a man of power no shame whether your infamy was your disbelief make life what you want it don't hustle to hard just look at the foo who doin time behind bars . No love for those who ain't paying my bills or who saved me from getting killed . In the hustle and grind time flys by when you got yo money coming in and out like yo bitches drawes fallen off like her papa didn't teach her laws . Bad cause of influence shit I even use to do it . Back than they called me that boy blasphemy no one knew why all I knew is that niggas wanted to blast at me funny tho these niggas scared rookies on streets so I never feared for my tragedies   . Life is a gimmick with one rhyme make money all time no rules fuck you for consisting me of making you a part of my team . Half wack niggas never held a heata so what you expect they gonna do when they pull up to the scene other niggas eager make yo shit wanna leave ya
